係公司好易扯旗 比其他同事唔小心掂到下面就會扯，見到人扯或者人地講咸野又會扯，好尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n平時都會一日打一次飛機 但係最近唔得 前日打仲打唔到任何野，之後去戒j 過左三日忍唔住又打 點知流啲透明液體出黎。。。<br />\n<br />\n平時個龜頭都幾大 所以打飛機個陣chok到嘅位好少<br />\n聽啲friend講佢地一次可以射好多 唔會好似我咁<br />\n打飛機個時都會幼想自己係a片裡面啲男主角 比人含 比人打飛機 比人插個啲<br />\n1.點先可以冇咁容易扯旗？<br />\n2.啲透明液體係啲咩黎？點解會流？<br />\n3. 有咩方法打飛機個陣興奮啲？射多啲？點樣加多啲幼想？<br />\n4. 食啲咩可以制多啲精？<br />\n5. 8cm夠唔夠長？<br />\n6. 扯旗唔直有冇影響"},{"pid":"309767ab8cd97bbb09bc3660bac929473805426f","tid":785121,"uid":168135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:39:53.000Z","msg":"識左幾耐先一齊 ?"},{"pid":"512e3a21e315f31b92213699ec8603eab8eed12e","tid":785121,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"証明你吸引力有限，佢騎牛揾馬。"},{"pid":"80216c29385593400439f480d7ccfc75a70c4152","tid":785121,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"746483da5a132e7435c1f23efd2b88990a90b44e","tid":785121,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3c931c9f089415b6d9a96ac7aa4c4aa045fc04","tid":785121,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"弘覺得呢啲關係好難keep大家又唔知對方背景 係講誠實<br />\n但而家佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:23:02.000Z","msg":"弘 你帽事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"弘say u<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae20917b34545f76f13dcd895e1c49d82eebad9","tid":785121,"uid":165186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:46:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪識玩囉 對話正常但識左先